    "name": {
      "zh": "Milkor M2A1榴弹发射器反射式瞄具",
      "en": "Milkor M2A1 grenade launcher reflex sight"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M2A1",
      "en": "M2A1"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "M2A1瞄具被设计用于弥补40毫米榴弹的下坠情况。内置的光线传感器可以在日间暗化瞄线，而在夜间行动时为瞄线补光。M2A1反射式瞄具提高了MUSA MSGL的易用度和实力。",
      "en": "The M2A1 sight was designed to compensate for the natural drift of the 40mm grenade. The built-in light sensor dims the reticle during daylight hours and allows for a brighter reticle during night time operations. The M2A1 reflex sight enhances the overall capabilities and usage of the MUSA MSGLs."
    },
